metadata.name: AI Junkies "Turquoise Bud"
metadata.created_by: The Undead Gaucho x Midjourney AI
metadata.description: Get ready to escape to a surreal world with "AI Junkies", the latest NFT collection from the talented artist, The Undead Gaucho. This collection takes you on a journey to the dystopian 80s future where aliens relax in the comfort of their own bedrooms. Each piece is a unique combination of the creative vision of The Undead Gaucho and the advanced technology of Midjourney AI. The result is a series of captivating NFTs, showcasing the aliens in their own personal worlds. Add to your NFT collection with these one-of-a-kind works of art and be a part of the future of digital art. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own a piece of art history, purchase your "AI Junkies" NFT today.
